авторизоваться с логином и паролем (??)
Log in to your server.
Log in to your system as the root user:
ssh root@server_ip_address

Create a new user account using the adduser command. like this adduser username, make password. And then add this new user to the sudo group
sudo su - username


Graphic session: log in with your username and password
SSH session: run ssh user@<ip-address-or-hostname> and enter your password
